an eye on him.
I'm sure you will.

503
00:54:26,997 --> 00:54:28,965
Is he the one, William?

504
00:54:30,700 --> 00:54:33,464
Is he?

505
00:54:33,536 --> 00:54:35,970
Only you can tell
for certain.

506
00:54:37,707 --> 00:54:41,108
Now, tomorrow night's
performance.

507
00:54:41,177 --> 00:54:44,408
Remember,
stay ahead of them.

508
00:54:44,481 --> 00:54:48,076
Keep the mystery,
always the mystery.

509
00:54:48,151 --> 00:54:50,085
[ Together ]
""Excess within control.""

510
00:54:56,726 --> 00:54:58,660
Sleep well,
McKenna.

