<i>Who is it?</i>

517
00:56:04,661 --> 00:56:06,595
Richard Collier.

518
00:56:13,036 --> 00:56:15,470
Good morning.

519
00:56:17,273 --> 00:56:19,707
<i>Um, you sleep all right?</i>

520
00:56:19,776 --> 00:56:22,870
Wonderfully.
<i>Oh, l'm sor</i>ry.

521
