554
00:58:08,351 --> 00:58:11,286
<i>[ People Chattering,</i>
<i>Laughing ]</i>

555
00:58:27,136 --> 00:58:30,071
Can I persuade you
to join me?

556
00:58:30,139 --> 00:58:32,607
Where are you from,
Collier ?

557
00:58:32,675 --> 00:58:35,940
