I presume you've written
more than one?

563
00:58:50,059 --> 00:58:52,084
Mmm.
And seen them produced.

564
00:58:52,161 --> 00:58:54,095
Really?
Mm-hmm.

565
00:58:54,163 --> 00:58:57,098
I'm not
entirely unacquainted
with the achievements...

566
00:58:57,166 --> 00:59:00,135
of the American stage
in the past decade.

567
00:59:00,203 --> 00:59:03,138
