when I arrived last night,
so I stayed with a friend.

587
01:00:03,299 --> 01:00:05,233
Ah, I see.

588
01:00:05,301 --> 01:00:08,099
Mm-hmm.
You do have a room, sir ?

589
01:00:08,171 --> 01:00:10,196
Oh, yes, yes.

590
